<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include('./module/website-info.ejs') %>
  <%- include('./module/general-link.ejs') %>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/client/product-detail.css">
</head>
 
<body>
  <%- include('./module/header.ejs') %>

  <section id="content">
    <section class="product bg-white rounded-1">
      <div class="product-img rounded-1">
        <div class="product-tag">
          <img id="product-tag-img">
        </div>
        <img id="product-img" class="rounded-2">
      </div>
      <div class="product-overview">
        <div class="product-overview-top">
          <div id="product-name" class="product-name large-primary-hightlight">
            Plantyou: 140+ Ridiculously Easy, Amazingly Delicious
            Plant-Based Oil-Free Recipes
          </div>
          <div class="product-information">
            <div class="product-information-item large-primary-hightlight">
              Category: Business
            </div>
            <div class="product-information-item large-primary-hightlight">
              Publish: Hachette Go - February 15, 2022
            </div>
            <div class="product-information-item large-primary-hightlight">
              Dimensions: 7.6 X 9.2 X 0.9 inches | 2.25 pounds
            </div>
            <div class="product-information-item large-primary-hightlight">
              Pages: 401
            </div>
            <div class="product-view">
              <div class="product-view-icon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="product-view-data">
                25
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="break-line">
        <div class="product-handle">
          <div class="product-choose-quantity-group">
            <div class="product-choose-quantity-title">
              Quantity
            </div>
            <div class="product-choose-quantity input-group">
              <button class="btn-square btn-primary">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
              </button>
              <input type="number" class="form-control" value="1">
              <button class="btn-square btn-primary">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-quantity-notification large-primary-hightlight">
            <span class="product-quantity fw-bold">
              5
            </span>
            products left
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="break-line">
        <div class="product-overview-bottom">
          <div class="product-price-group">
            <div class="product-price">
              $27.60
            </div>
            <div class="product-sale">
              15%
            </div>
            <div class="product-old-price">
              $27.60
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-interaction">
            <button class="btn-primary text-uppercase ms-2 me-2">
              Add to cart
            </button>
            <button class="btn-success text-uppercase ms-2 me-2">
              Buy now
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="product-description bg-white rounded-2">
      <div class="product-description-title">
        Description
      </div>
      <div class="product-description-content">
        Plant-based eating doesn't have to be complicated! The delicious recipes in this easy-to-follow cookbook are
        guaranteed to keep you inspired and motivated.

        Enter PlantYou, the ridiculously easy plant-based, oil-free cookbook with over 140+ healthy vegan recipes for
        breakfast, lunch, dinner, cheese sauces, salad dressings, dessert and more!
        In her eagerly anticipated debut cookbook, Carleigh Bodrug, the Founder of the wildly popular social media
        community PlantYou, provides readers with the ultimate full color guidebook that makes plant-based meal
        planning, grocery shopping and cooking a breeze. With every single recipe, you will find a visual infographic
        marking the ingredients you need, making it easy to shop, determine portion sizes, and dive into the delicious
        and nutritious dishes.
        Get ready for mouthwatering dishes like Chocolate Chip Banana Bread Breakfast Cookies, Best Ever Cauli Wings,
        and the Big BOSS Burrito that you simply won't believe are made from plants.
        "An instant kitchen classic...In your quest to find delicious food that also promotes health, both human health
        and the health of the planet and the animals we share our world with, you've come to the right place."
        --from the foreword by Dr. Will Bulsiewicz
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>

  <%- include('./module/footer.ejs') %>

  <script type="module" src="/javascripts/client/product-detail.js"></script>
</body>

</html>